cription><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/14/DSC02615.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/14/DSC02615.jpg"><media:title>2026 Rifle NCAA National Champions</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/14/DSC02615.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 15:39:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>8</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58864</s:story_id></item><item><title>First Round NCAA Tournament Games Sold Out</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/20/womens-basketball-first-round-ncaa-tournament-games-sold-out</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/20/womens-basketball-first-round-ncaa-tournament-games-sold-out</guid><category>Women's Basketball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="NCAA First Round Sold Out" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/20/WBB_MMRD1SOLDOUT_1920x1080_.png" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The Mountaineer Ticket Office has announced that the women's basketball March Madness first round games at Hope Coliseum on Saturday, March 21 are sold out.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/20/WBB_MMRD1SOLDOUT_1920x1080_.png" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/20/WBB_MMRD1SOLDOUT_1920x1080_.png"><media:title>NCAA First Round Sold Out</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/20/WBB_MMRD1SOLDOUT_